    dc:description "FIGURES 86 ─ 97. Regalana uni sp. nov., holotype male. 86, head and thorax, dorsal view. 87, head, frontal view. 88, head and thorax, lateral view. 89, forewing, dorsal view. 90 ─ 97, male terminalia: 90, sternite VIII, ventral view. 91, pygofer and subgenital plate, lateral view. 92, subgenital plate, ventral view. 93, style and connective, dorsal view. 94, style, lateral view. 95, aedeagus, lateral view. 96, aedeagus, posterior view. 97, aedeagus, dorsal view. Scale bars in mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/251974/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

